title: Former U.S. President Obama visits New Zealand, meets PM Ardern
text:
Former U.S. President Obama visits New Zealand, meets PM Ardern 3:26am EDT - 01:15 
Barack Obama is welcomed to New Zealand with a traditional Maori ceremony alongside the country's leader Jacinda Ardern. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
